parameters: It's rough times for bounty hunters like myself.
With Aldreith's experimentation taking fold, the
quantity of game to hunt has died off.
Maybe it's time I took up another job.
The "town" has been deserted ever since Aldreith
commenced his operations to expand his military
With no animals left to hunt, the citizens were left
with no choice but to relocate elsewhere.
The remaining citizens have resorted to opening up
shops consisting of potions and weaponry.
Travelers tend to stop by Lunk Town to pick up
any stock that needs resupplying, so business works
